*Traži* ga po celom gradu. (He is looking for him in the whole city.)

Ona *traži* svoju knjigu. (She is looking for her book.)

Mnogi ljudi *traže* odgovor. (Many people are looking for an answer.)

On *traži* da mu se pridruži. (He is asking to join him.)

Oni *traže* novi posao. (They are looking for a new job.)

Mi smo *tražili* odgovore. (We were looking for answers.)